<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="102" type="reference_group">
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="102">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Feuillet" authorityYear="2016" baseAuthorityName="Feuillet" baseAuthorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Heliotropiaceae" genus="Tournefortia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Tournefortia humilis" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humilis" status="comb. nov.">Tournefortia humilis</taxonomicName>
L., Sp. Pl.: 141. 1753. Type. &quot; 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Feuillet" authorityYear="2016" baseAuthorityName="Feuillet" baseAuthorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Heliotropiaceae" genus="Tournefortia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Tournefortia foliis subsp. lanceolatis" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="foliis" status="comb. nov." subSpecies="lanceolatis">Tournefortia foliis lanceolatis</taxonomicName>
&quot; pl. by Plumier, in Burman, Pl. Amer., 224, t. 227, f. 2. 1760 (lectotype designated by Miller in 
<bibRefCitation author="Cafferty, S" journalOrPublisher="Taxon" pageId="10" pageNumber="111" pagination="799 - 805" publicationUrl="10.2307/4135454" refId="B3" refString="Cafferty, S, Jarvis, CE, 2004. Typification of Linnaean plant names in Boraginaceae. Taxon 53 (3): 799 - 805, DOI: 10.2307/4135454" title="Typification of Linnaean plant names in Boraginaceae." url="10.2307/4135454" volume="53" year="2004">Cafferty and Jarvis 2004</bibRefCitation>
, pg. 804). Epitype: FRANCE. Martinique: Case Pilote, Feb 1868, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">L. Hahn 416</emphasis>
(designated by Miller in 
<bibRefCitation author="Cafferty, S" journalOrPublisher="Taxon" pageId="10" pageNumber="111" pagination="799 - 805" publicationUrl="10.2307/4135454" refId="B3" refString="Cafferty, S, Jarvis, CE, 2004. Typification of Linnaean plant names in Boraginaceae. Taxon 53 (3): 799 - 805, DOI: 10.2307/4135454" title="Typification of Linnaean plant names in Boraginaceae." url="10.2307/4135454" volume="53" year="2004">Cafferty and Jarvis 2004</bibRefCitation>
, pg. 804: BM n.v.).
</paragraph>
